| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3066 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 39cb71b0-1755-5593-8d2f-91c07232d6aa"
